FBIS3-56931 "drsov014_a_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Secretary Bentsen Buys Share in Candy Factory PM2001103794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 20 Jan 94 First Edition p 1 PM2001103794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Item from roundup of ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA, ITAR-TASS reports under the "Yesterday, Today, Tomorrow" rubric: "U.S. Minister Is Our Shareholder"] [Text] U.S. Secretary of the Treasury Lloyd Bentsen has set a good example for businessmen who still cannot make up their minds to invest their capital in Russia. Visiting the capital's "Red October" Confectionery Factory in the framework of the U.S. President's official visit to Russia, he acquired a share in this enterprise.
